thread.title: Svetlana Sally Johnston
thread.title_full: Mobile-Mate reviewed by Svetlana Sally Johnston

author: Svetlana Sally Johnston
title: Svetlana Sally Johnston
text:
I was very apprehensive about making an online purchased but as it turned out I did not need to be.
I ordered on 13th March and on 16th March I was holding my order in my hot little hands, despite Australia Post mucking things up a little.
Mobile Mate you guys ROCK!
Thanks bunches for a great shopping experience.
